ZH: 请你手下留情，不要太严厉惩罚他。
EN: Please show mercy and don't punish him too severely.

ZH: 我知道你很生气，但是请手下留情，不要伤害别人。
EN: I know you're very angry, but please be merciful and don't hurt others.

ZH: 这次我犯了错，希望你能手下留情。
EN: I made a mistake this time, I hope you can show mercy.

ZH: 力量大的人应该学会手下留情。
EN: People with power should learn to show mercy.

ZH: 即使你很生气，也要记得手下留情。
EN: Even if you're very angry, remember to show mercy.

ZH: 在这种情况下，手下留情是最好的选择。
EN: In this situation, showing mercy is the best choice.

ZH: 我求求你，手下留情吧。
EN: I beg you, please show mercy.

ZH: 虽然他犯了错，但是我希望你手下留情。
EN: Although he made a mistake, I hope you will be merciful.

ZH: 他错了，但是希望你还能手下留情。
EN: He was wrong, but I hope you can still be merciful.

ZH: 请你手下留情，不要太过严厉。
EN: Please show mercy, don't be too harsh.

ZH: 这是一次大意的失误，请手下留情。
EN: This was a careless mistake, please show mercy.

ZH: 我请求你手下留情，考虑一下他的处境。
EN: I ask you to show mercy, consider his situation.

ZH: 请你手下留情，不要太过苛刻。
EN: Please show mercy, don't be too demanding.

ZH: 尽管他犯了错，但是我还是请求你手下留情。
EN: Even though he made a mistake, I still ask you to show mercy.

ZH: 他虽然做了错事，但是希望你还是能手下留情。
EN: Although he did something wrong, I hope you can still show mercy.

ZH: 在这种情况下，手下留情是最好的选择。
EN: In this situation, showing mercy is the best choice.

ZH: 我知道你有理由生气，但是请求你手下留情。
EN: I know you have every reason to be angry, but I beg you to show mercy.

ZH: 他已经意识到自己的错误，请你手下留情。
EN: He has realized his mistake, please show mercy.

ZH: 请你手下留情，考虑一下他的意图。
EN: Please show mercy, consider his intentions.
